\SE[4]Ryan? Did you come to witness my pride? \SE[0]Be
envious as I, the adorable me, have obtained the weapon
called magic and have become overwhelmingly strongest.

\SE[11]He's not here...!! \!\SE[14]I came all this way to
show off... but he's not here!!

\SE[29]Why is he always like this?! \SE[27]He always messes

down, Rebecca... I'm a maiden... a maiden that everyone

\SE[2]... That's unlikely. Considering his sense of style.

floating...? \!\SE[2]I wonder if something is stuck in

Attack while you have the chance...?)
